   Pea ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ fjjskfqfap klv akglyaZ Xy Yfqfzakp lb qea
OqWqap Yljmlpfkd qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, veaqeao Wp Yfqfzakp lb qea OqWqap
lo lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, lofdfkWqaZ fk ofdeqp mlppappaZ lo YiWfjaZ Xy
qea fkeWXfqWkqp lb qea qefoqaak AjaofYWk Ylilkfap, vefia qeay vaoa
ZamakZakYfap lb CoaWq cofqWfk. Pea pqosddia lb qea AjaofYWk Ylilkfpqp
blo fkZamakZakYa vWp XWpaZ smlk qea YiWfj qeWq qeay vaoa ZakfaZ, Xy qea
mWoakq dltaokjakq, ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ fjjskfqfap vefYe vaoa qeafo
Yljjlk eaofqWda Wp cofqfpe boaajak, lo vefYe eWZ bolj qfja ql qfja Xaak
doWkqaZ pmaYfbfYWiiy ql qea AjaofYWk Ylilkfap. 
   Jl vofqqak YeWoq fk awfpqakYa, qeak lo klv, eWp atao WqqajmqaZ ql
aksjaoWqa, YiWofby, WkZ Zabfka fk lka psYYfkYq awmoappflk, qea ofdeqp,
ifXaoqfap, WkZ boWkYefpap mlppappaZ Xy xkdifpe psXgaYqp, klo fp fq qea
msomlpa lb qefp tlisja ql Wqqajmq ql Zl qeWq. Eq fp psbbfYfakq ql pWy
qeWq qea ifXaoqfap WkZ ofdeq lb paib-dltaokjakq lb qea cofqfpe malmia,
Xadfkkfkd vfqe qea ZaYiWoWqflkp lb IWdkW reWoqW, eWta Xaak WpYaoqWfkaZ
WkZ ZaYiWoaZ bolj qfja ql qfja, Zsofkd pfw Yakqsofap lb YlkbifYq Xaqvaak
qea malmia lb qea cofqfpe oaWij WkZ qeafo psYYappfta pltaoafdkp, skqfi
qeay Woa klv vaii apqWXifpeaZ WkZ nsfqa qelolsdeiy skZaopqllZ. 
   JlqvfqepqWkZfkd qea cofqfpe malmia eWta oaqWfkaZ fk qeafo dltaokjakq
qea bloj lb W ifjfqaZ jlksoYey, qeay eWta apqWXifpeaZ blo qeajpaitap Wp
WdWfkpq qeafo YlkpqfqsqflkWi jlkWoYe, W jaWpsoa lb mlmsiWo pltaoafdkqy
WkZ maoplkWi ifXaoqy Wp doaWq Wp qeWq mlppappaZ Xy Wky lqeao malmia fk
qea vloiZ. Kso XlWpq fp qeWq lsop fp W boaa oamsXifY; qeWq fq fp
ZlsXqbsi veaqeao, Wiqelsde va eWta W moapfZakq fkpqaWZ lb W hfkd, WkZ
W psmoaja Ylsoq vfqe aaoqsfk mlvao ql Ylkqoli Xlqe awaYsqfta WkZ
iadfpiWqfta WYqflk, qea Gfkd lb xkdiWkZ, lk qea velia, mlppappap Wp jsYe
fkZamakZakq Wsqelofqy Wp qea LoapfZakq lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap. 
   Aiqelsde qea pqosddia lb qea AjaofYWk Ylilkfpqp vWp XWpaZ smlk qea
YiWfj qeWq qea mWoakq dltaokjakq ZakfaZ qea fkeWXfqWkqp lb qea Ylilkfap
