skZao cofqfpe Zljfkflk, vaoa WYYloZaoaZ WkZ WYqsWiiy akglyaZ jWky
ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ boWkYefpap, maYsifWo ql qeajpaitap, klq akglyaZ
