fqp lofdfkWi paqqiajakq WkZ dltaokjakq. Eq fp miWfk ql paa, Xy
YljmWofplk vfqe lqeao efpqlofY ZlYsjajqp, qeWq qea uaYiWoWqflk lb
EkZamakZakYa lb 1776 vWp jlZaiaZ, ql W iWoda awqakq, klq smlk xkdifpe
moaYaZakqp, Xsq smlk qea vofqqak Ylkpqfqsqflk lb qea JaqeaoiWkZp
NamsXifY, YWiiaZ Pea Qkflk lb QqoaYeq, lb 1579. 
   Pea jWkfbapql fppsaZ Xy qea oaXaip Wq qea qfja lb cWYlk'p NaXaiiflk
fk RfodfkfW fk 1676 YlkqWfkp jsYe bolj qea pWja plsoYa. Pea Qkflk lb
