ql Wp qea plsoYa bolj vefYe qea YiWfj paq bloqe fk qea uaYiWoWqflk lb
EkZamakZakYa vaoa ZaoftaZ. 
   Jlo ZfZ qea AjaofYWk fZaWp lb W vofqqak Ylkqfqfqsqflk WkZ W psmoaja
Ylsoq ajWkWqa Wiqldaqeao bolj xkdifpejak. Peay vaoa qea oapsiqp lb qea
