Ylkqakqflk. Oea WXlifpeaZ qfqeap WkZ blobafqaZ diaXa iWkZp. Pea YeWkda
vWp Xolsdeq WXlsq qeolsde qea fkbisakYa lb LWqofYh Dakoy, W OYlqYe
Zfppakqao; WkZ lb PeljWp Fabbaoplk, W jWk lb Saipe lofdfk, vfqe tfavp
