fk qea usqYe Ylilky lb Jav Uloh WkZ fk qea MsWhao Ylilky lb
LakkpyitWkfW. 
   Ol, qll, qea AjaofYWk Yfqfzak ZaoftaZ efp mofkYfmiap lb oaifdflsp
qliaoWqflk, klq bolj xkdiWkZ, Xsq bolj qea usqYe. Ap iWqa Wp 1663, veak
