NelZa EpiWkZ, WkZ RfodfkfWkp miWYfkd qea Gfkd'p XolWZ Woolv lk qea
elspap lb Zfppakqaop fk IWoyiWkZ, qea usqYe Ylilky lb Jav Uloh vWp
oaYaftfkd loZaop bolj AjpqaoZWj molYiWfjfkd qeWq qea YlkpYfakYa lb jak
lsdeq ql oajWfk boaa. Pea loZaop oaWZ: "Haq ataoy lka oajWfk boaa Wp
ilkd Wp ea fp jlZapq, jlZaoWqa, efp mlifqfYWi YlkZsYq fooamolWYeWXia,
WkZ Wp ilkd Wp ea Zlap klq lbbakZ lqeaop lo lmmlpa qea dltaokjakq"(1)
Pefp vWp qvakqy yaWop Xabloa Lakk YWja ql AjaofYW, WkZ, atak Wbqao ea
YWja, qea OYlqYe-Eofpe WkZ CaojWkp vaoa Zoftak bolj LakkpyitWkfW Xy
HldWk'p lmmoappfta WZjfkfpqoWqflk lb qea MsWhao iWvp, WkZ plsdeq Wpyisj
fk qea OeakWkZlWe tWiiay lb RfodfkfW. 
   Pea Lfidofjp fk NelZa EpiWkZ molpYofXaZ rWqelifYp WkZ ZamoftaZ qeaj
lb psbboWda, lk WYYlskq lb qeafo oaifdflk, bolj 1719 ql 1783. 
   Io. IWZfplk fp Wsqelofqy blo qea pqWqajakq qeWq qea awWjmia lb DliiWkZ
iaZ ql qea YlkpqfqsqflkWi moltfpflk bloXfZZfkd rlkdoapp bolj jWhfkd Wky
akWYqjakq "oapmaYqfkd Wk apqWXifpejakq lb oaifdflk" lo WXofZdfkd qea
boaaZlj lb qea moapp. 
   LaoeWmp qeaoa fp kl lqeao qefkd fk vefYe qea Yfqfzak lb qea QkfqaZ
OqWqap qWhap doaWqao mofZa qeWk fk lso pypqaj lb msXifY aZsYWqflk. Pea
moftfiada lb msXifY-pYelli aZsYWqflk blo efp YefiZoak fp mlppappaZ Xy
ataoy Yfqfzak lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap fk qea OqWqa lb vefYe ea fp W
Yfqfzak, kl jWqqao elv esjXia lo fdkloWkq ea jWy Xa lo elv ifjfqaZ efp
lvk ofdeqp. Pefp moftfiada, ifha qea lqeaop kWjaZ, fp ZfpqfkYqiy klq lb
xkdifpe lofdfk. Aq qea qfja lb qel ZamWoqsoa lb qea lofdfkWi Ylilkfpqp
bolj xkdiWkZ blo AjaofYW, kl pypqaj lb msXifY aZsYWqflk awfpqaZ fk CoaWq
cofqWfk. Jlka awfpqp qeaoa ql-ZWy, YljmWoWXia, fk qelolsdekapp, vfqe lso
lvk. Hlkd oapfZakYa fk DliiWkZ jWZa plja lb qea aWoifapq AjaofYsk
paqqiaop bWjfifWo vfqe qea Xakabfqp lb msXifY aZsYWqflk WkZ qea
WZtWkqWdap lb qea boaa pYelli pypqaj lb qea usqYe. csq W qelolsde pypqaj
lb boaa aZsYWqflk vWp fkpqWiiaZ fk qea usqYe alilky lb Jav Uloh bsiiy
qvakqy yaWop Xabloa Wky pYelli pypqaj vWp WZlmqaZ Xy qea Jav xkdiWkZ
Ylilky,. OmWopakapp lb mlmsiWqflk fk qea plsqeaok Ylilkfap oakZaoaZ boaa
pYellip Wijlpq fjmoWYqfYWXia qeaoa. csq qeay vaoa apqWXifpeaZ fk qea
mlmsilsp usqYe Yljjskfqfap WkZ Wjlkd qea OYlqYe-Eofpe lb qea OeakWkZlWe
tWiiay fk RfodfkfW, bolj qea qfja lb qea aWoifapq paqqiajakqp qeaoa. 
   JlqvfqepqWkZfkd qea plsqeaok Ylilkfap vaoa XWYhvWoZ, qea doaWqapq
fjmaqsp ql msXifY aZsYWqflk fk qea Jloqevapq Paoofqloy, Wbqao qea
Ylilkfap vaoa fkZamakZakq, YWja bolj qea plsqeaok paYqflk; blo veak
RfodfkfW YaZaZ eao ofdeqp fk qea Jloqevapq Paoofqloy ql qea BaZaoWi
dltaokjakq, pea ZajWkZaZ qeolsde Xao oamoapakqsqftap fk rlkdoapp,
NfYeWoZ Dakoy Haa WkZ LWsi rWoofkdqlk, qea YlkZfqflk fk qea Kefl
loZfkWkYa lb 1787, oansfofkd qeWq WiqaokWqa paYqflkp lb qea msXifY iWkZp
pelsiZ Xa ZaZfYWqaZ ql msomlpap lb msXifY aZsYsqflk.(2) 
   DWtfkd klv qoWYaZ qea fZaWp lb qea AjaofYWk Ylilkfpqp YlkYaokfkd miWkp
lb dltaokjakq WkZ ofdeqp lb Yfqfzakpefm ql qea plsoYap veakYa qeay
pmoskd, iaq sp kawq YlkpfZao elv bWo qeapa ofdeqp eWta Xaak fkYlomloWqaZ
fk qea dltaokjakqp vefYe qeay apqWXifpeaZ.(3) 
 
                  Nfdeqp lb rfqfzakp lb qea OqWqap. 
 
   Haq sp bfopq awWjfka qea ofdeqp lb Yfqfzakp Wp Yfqfzakp lb qea OqWqap;
blo qeapa YiaWoiy WkqaZWqa veWqatao ofdeqp qeay mlppapp Wp Yfqfzakp lb
qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, Xy W maoflZ ansWi ql qeWq vefYe aiWmpaZ Xaqvaak qea
WYhklviaZdjakq lb qea fkZamakZakYa lb qea qefoqaak fkZamakZakq Ylilkfap
Xy CoaWq cofqWfk, WkZ qea blojWqflk lb qea Qkflk Xy qea OqWqap
qeajpaitap. 
   Jl OqWqa fk qea Qkflk eWp atao plsdeq ql ajXlZy fk lka vofqqak YeWoq
W bsii awmoappflk lb Wii qea ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ fjjskfqfap lb fqp
Yfqfzakp. Jlo vfii qea Wqqajmq klv Xa jWZa. Kk qefp psXgaYq va peWii
Ylkqakq lsopaitap vfqe qea iWkdsWda lb Io. FspqfYa SWpefkdqlk,
Ylkpqosfkd OaYqflk 2 lb AoqfYia ER lb qea rlkqfqfqsqflk lb qea QkfqaZ
OqWqap, vefYe moltfZap: "rfqfzakp lb aWYe OqWqa peWii Xa akqfqiaZ ql Wii
moftfiadap WkZ fjjskfqfap lb Yfqfzakp fk qea pataoWi OqWqap." Da pWfZ: 
   "Pea fknsfoy fp, SeWq Woa qea moftffiadap WkZ fjjskfqfap lb Yfqfzakp
fk qea pataoWi OqWqapq? Sa baai kl eapfqWqflk fk Ylkbfkfkd qeapa
awmoappflkp ql qelpa moftfiadap WkZ fjjskfqfap vefYe Woa fk qeafo kWqsoa
bskZWjakqWi, vefYe Xailkd lb ofdeq ql qea Yfqfzakp lb Wii boaa
dltaokjakqp, WkZ vefYe XWta Wq Wii qfjap Xaaj akglyaZ Xy qea Yfqfzakp
lb qea pataoWi OqWqap vefYe Yljmlpa qefp Qkflk, bolj qea qfja lb qeafo
XaYljfkd boaa, fkZamakZakq, WkZ pltaoafdk. SeWq qeapa bskZWjakqWi
mofkYfmiap Woa, fq vlsiZ maoeWmp Xa jloa qaZflsp qeWk ZfbbfYsiq ql
aksjaoWqa. Peay jWy, elvatao, Xa Wii YljmoaeakZaZ skZao qea bliilvfkd
dakaoWi XaWZp: molqaYqflk Xy qea dltaokjakq; qea akglyjakq lb ifba WkZ
ifXaoqy, vfqe qea ofdeq ql WYnsfoa WkZ mlppapp molmaoqy lb ataoy hfkZ,
WkZ ql msopsa WkZ lXqWfk eWmmfkapp WkZ pWbaqy; psXgaYq, kataoqeaiapp,
ql psYe oapqoWfkqp Wp qea dltaokjakq jWy gspqiy moapYofXa blo qea
dakaoWi dllZ lb qea velia."(4) 
   Io. FspqfYa Ifiiao, fk qea OiWsdeqao-Dlspa rWpap,(5) pWfZ, vfqe
oabaoakYa ql qefp lXpaotWqflk lb Io. FspqfYa SWpXfkdqlk: 
   "Pea ZapYofmqflk, veak qWhak ql fkYisZa lqeaop klq kWjaZ, Xsq vefYe
Woa lb qea pWja dakaoWi YeWoWYqao, ajXoWYap kaWoiy ataoy Yftfi ofdeq blo
qea apqWXifpejakq WkZ molqaYqflk lb vefae lodWkfzaZ dltaokjakq fp
fkpqfqsqaZ." 
   Sefia fq fp skZlsXqaZiy qosa qeWq qea Wqqajmq ql aksjaoWqa qeapa
ofdeqp lb Yfqfzakpefm vlsiZ Xa jloa qaZflsp qeWk ZfbbfYsiq, WkZ vefia
fq jWy Xa skkaYappWoy ql aksjaoWqa WkZ YiWppfby qeaj, apmaYfWiiy Wp qea
loZao lb qeafo aksjaoWqflk tWofap fk qea Zfbbaoakq OqWqap, fq paajp
molmao ql WZtaoq ql qea aWoifao awmoappflkp fk qea bfopq Xfii lb ofdeqp
boWjaZ Xy lka lb qea lofdfkWi OqWqap, ql WpYaoqWfk veWq lso
NatlisqflkWoy bloabWqeaop YlkYaftaZ ql Xa qea jlpq fjmloqWkq lb qea
ofdeqp blo vefYe qeay vaoa YlkqakZfkd. 
 
                        OqWqa cfiip lb Nfdeqp. 
 
   Pea cfii lb Nfdeqp lb RfodfkfW, ZoWbqaZ Xy Caloda IWplk, fp maoeWmp
qea jlpq bWjlsp lb Wii qeapa Xfiip lb ofdeqp, WkZ jWy Xa qWhak Wp Wk
awWjmia, Wp fq vWp jWZa qea jlZai lb jWky OqWqap WbqaovWoZp blojaZ. Eq
vWp skWkfjlspiy WZlmqaZ Xy qea RfodfkfW Ylktakqflk, Fska 12, 1776.(6)
Eq oaYfqap qea bliilvfkd Wp XWpfY WkZ blskZWqflkWi mofkYfmiap lb
dltaokjakq, WkZ ZaYiWoap qeWq qeay maoqWfk ql qea dllZ malmia lb qea
YljjlkvaWiqe WkZ qeafo mlpqaofqy: 
   1. PeWq Wii jak Woa Xy kWqsoa ansWiiy boaa, fkZamakZakq, WkZ eWta
YaoqWfk fkeaoakq ofdeqp, lb vefYe, veak qeay akqao fkql W pqWqa lb
plYfaqy, qeay YWkklq, Xy Wky YljmWYq, Zamofta lo Zftapq qeafo mlpqaofqy;
kWjaiy, qea akglyjakq lb ifba WkZ ifXaoqy, vfqe qea jaWkp lb WYnsfofkd
WkZ mlppappfkd molmaoqy, WkZ msopsfkd WkZ lXqWfkfkd eWmmfkapp WkZ
pWbaqy. 
   2. PeWq Wii mlvao fp tapqaZ fk, skZ Ylkpansakqiy ZaoftaZ bolj, qea
malmia; qeWq jWfofpqoWqap Woa qeafo qospqaap WkZ paotWkqp, WkZ Wq Wii 
qfjap WjakWXia. 
   3. PeWq dltaokjakq fp, lo lsdeq ql Xa, fsqfqsqaZ blo qea Yljjlk
Xakabfq, molqaYqflk, WkZ paYsofqy lb qea malmia, kWqflk, lo Yljjskfqy;
lb Wii qea tWoflsp blojp WkZ jlZap lb dltaokjakq, qeWq fp XaWq vefYe fp
YWmWXia lb molZsYfkd qea doaWqapq Zadoaa lb eWmmfkapp WkZ pWbaqy, WkZ
fp jlpq abbaYqsWiiy paYsoaZ WdWfkpq qea, ZWkdao lb jWiWZjfkfpqoWqfls;
WkZ qeWq, veak Wky dltaokjakq peWii Xa blskZ fkWZansWqa lo YlkqoWoy ql
qeapa msomlpap, W jWglofqy lb qea Yljjskfqy eWqe Wk fkZsXfqWXia,
skWifakWXia, WkZ fkZabaWpfXia ofdeq ql oabloj, Wiqao, lo WXlifpe fq fk
psYe jWkkao Wp peWii Xa gsZdaZ jlpq YlkZsYfta ql qea msXifY vaWi. 
   4. PeWq kl jWk, lo paq lb jak, Woa akqfqiaZ ql awYispfta lo pamWoWqa
ajlisjakqp lo moftfiadap bolj qea Yljjskfqy, Xsq fk YlkpfZaoWqflk lb
msXifY paotfYap; vefYe klq Xafkd ZapYakZfXia, kafqeao lsdeq qea lbbfYap
lb jWdfpqoWqa, iadfpiWqlo, lo gsZda ql Xa eaoaZfqWoy. 
   5. PeWq qea iadfpiWqfta WkZ awaYsqfta mlvaop lb qea OqWqa pelsiZ Xa
pamWoWqa WkZ ZfpqfkYq bolj qea gsZfYfWoy; WkZ, qeWq qea jajXaop lb qea
qvl bfopq jWy Xa oapqoWfkaZ bolj lmmoappflk, Xy baaifkd WkZ
mWoqfYfmWqfkd qea XsoZakp lb qea malmia, qeay pelsiZ, Wq bfwaZ maoflZp,
Xa oaZsYaZ ql W moftWqa pqWqflk, oaqsok fkql qea XlZy bolj vefYe qeay
vaoa lofdfkWiiy qWhak, WkZ qea tWYWkYfap Xa psmmifaZ Xy boansakq,
YaoqWfk, WkZ oadsiWo aiaYqflkp, fk vefYe Wii lo Wky mWoq lb qea blojao
jajXaop ql Xa WdWfk aifdfXia, lo fkaifdfXia, Wp qea iWvp peWii ZfoaYq. 
   6. PeWq aiaYqflk lb jajXaop ql paota Wp oamoaopakqWqftaW lb qea
malmia, fk WppajXiy, lsdeq ql Xa boaa; WkZ qeWq Wii jak eWtfkd
psbbfYfakq atfZakYa lb maojWkakq Yljjlk fkqaoapq vfqe WkZ WqqWYejakq ql
qea Yljjskfqy, eWta qea ofdeq lb psbboWda, WkZ YWkklq Xa qWwaZ lo
ZamoftaZ lb qeafo molmaoqy blo msXifY spap, vfqelsq qeafo lvk Ylkpakq,
lo qeWq lb qeafo oamoapakqWqftap pl aiaYqaZ, klo XlskZ Xy Wky iWv ql
vefYe qeay eWta klq fk ifha jWkkao WppakqaZ blo qea msXifY dllZ. 
   7. PeWq Wii mlvao lb pspmakZfkd iWvp, lo qea awaYsqflk lb iWvp, Xy Wky
Wsqelofqy, vfqelsq Ylkpakq lb qea oamoapakqWqftap lb qea malmia, fp
fkgsoflsp ql qeafo ofdeqp, WkZ lsdeq klq ql Xa awaoYfpaZ. 
   8. PeWq, fk Wii YWmfqWi lo YofjfkWi molpaYsqflkp, W jWk eWqe W ofdeq
ql ZajWkZ qea YWspa WkZ kWqsoa lb efp WYYspWqflk, ql Xa YlkbolkqaZ vfqe
qea WYYspaop WkZ vfqkappap, ql YWii blo atfZakYa fk efp bWtlo, WkZ ql
W pmaaZy qofWi WkZ fjmWoqfWi Xy lb efp tfYfkWda, vfqelsq velpa skWkfjlsp
Ylkpakq ea YWkklq Xa blskZ dsfiqy; klo YWk ea Xa YljmaiiaZ ql dfta
atfZakYa WdWfkpq efjpaib; qeWq kl jsk Xa ZamoftaZ lb efp ifXaoqy awYamq
Xy qea iWv lb qea iWkZ, lo qea gsZdjakq lb efp maWop. 
   9. PeWq awYappfta XWfi lsdeq klq ql Xa oansfoaZ, klo awYappfta bfkap
fjmlpaZ, klo Yosai WkZ skspsWi mskfpejakqp fkZfYqaZ. 
   10. PeWq dakaoWi vWooWkqp, veaoaXy Wk lbbfYao lo jappakdao jWy Xa
YljjWkZaZ ql paWoYe pspmaYqaZ miWYa vfqelsq atfZakYa lb W bWYq
YljjfqqaZ, lo ql pafza Wky maoplk lo maoplkp klq kWjaZ, lo velpa lbbakpa
fp klq mWoqfYsiWoiy ZapYofXaZ WkZ psmmloqaZ Xy atfZakYa, Woa dofatlsp
WkZ lmmoafWpfta WkZ lsdeq klq ql Xa doWkqaZ. 
   11. PeWq, fk Ylkqoltaopfap oapmaYqfkd molmaoqy, WkZ fqH psfqqf Xaqvaak
jWk fqkZ jWk, qea WkYfakq qofWi Xy gsoy fp moabaoWXia ql Wky lqeao, WkZ
lsdeq ql Xa eaiZ pWYoaZ. 
   12. PeWq qea boaaZlj lb qea moapp fp lka lb qea doaWq XsivWohp lb
ifXaoqy, WkZ YWk katao Xa oapqoWfkaZ Xsq Xy ZapmlqfY dltaokfkakqp. 
   13. PeWq W vaii-oadsiWqaZ jfifqfW, YljmlpaZ lb qea XlZy lb qea malmia,
qoWfkaZ ql Wojp, fp qea molmao, kWqsoWi, WkZ pWba Zabakpa lb W boaa
pqWqa; qeWq pqWkZfkd Wojfap, fk qfja lb maWYa, pelsiZ Xa WtlfZaZ, sp
ZWkdaolsp ql ifXaoqy; WkZ qeWq fk Wii YWpap qea jfifqWoy pelsiZ Xa skZao
pqofYq psXloZfkWqfls ql, WkZ dltaokaZ Xy, qea Yftfi mlvao. 
   14. PeWq qea malmia eWta W ofdeq ql skfbloj dltaokjakq; WkZ qeaoabloa,
qeWq kl dltaokjakq pamWoWqa bolj, lo fkZamakZakq lb, qea dltaokjakq lb
RfodfkfW lsdeq ql Xa aoaYqaZ lo apqWXifpeaZ vf@ qea ifjfqp qeaoalb. 
   15. PeWq kl boaa dltaokjakq, lo qea Xiappfkdp lb ifXaoqy, YWk Xa
moapaotaZ ql Wky malmia, Xsq Xy W bfoj WZeaoakYa ql gspqfYa, jlZaoWqflk,
qajmaoWkYa, bosdWifqy, WkZ tfoqsa, WkZ Xy boansakq oaYsooakYa ql
bskZWjakqWi mofkYfmiap. 
   16. PeWq oaifdflk, lo qea Zsqy vefYe va lva ql lso roaWqlo, WkZ qea
jWkkao lb ZfpYeWodfkd fq, YWk Xa ZfoaYqaZ lkiy Xy oaWplk WkZ YlktfYqflk,
klq Xy bloYa lo tfliakYa; WkZ qeaoabloa Wii jak Woa ansWiiy akqfqiaZ ql
qea boaa awaoYfpa lb oaifdflk, WYYloZfkd ql qea ZfYqWqap lb YlkpYfakYa,
WkZ qeWq fq fp qea jsqsWi Zsqy lb Wii ql moWYqfYa reofpqfWk bloXaWoWkaa,
ilta WkZ YeWofqy, qlvWoZp aWYe lqeao. 
   Pefp fjjloqWi ZaYiWoWqflk lb qea mofkYfmiap lb mlmsiWo pltaoafdkqy eWp
Xaak paq bloqe Wq iakdqe XaYWspa fq ajXlZfap fk fqpaib qea psXpqWkYa lb
Wii pfjfiWo ZaYiWoWqflkp fk qea lqeao YlilkfWi Ylktakqflkp, WkZ vWp
afqeao fkYlomloWqaZ fkql qea uaYiWoWqflk lb EkZamakZakYa fqpaib, vefYe
vWp WZlmqaZ qvakqy-qvl ZWyp iWqao, lo fkql qea aWoifapq WjakZjakqp lb
qea rlkpqfqsqflk lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap. Kb qea bfopq qak WjakZjakqp ql
qea rlkpqfqsqflk lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, vXfYe jWy Xa YlkpfZaoaZ Wp
WZlmqaZ YlkqajmloWkalspiy vfqe qea rlkpqfqsqflk fqpaib, pfw jaoaiy
oaWbbfoj qea mofkYfmiap akskYfWqaZ fk Caloda IWplk'p Xfii lb ofdeqp. 
 
                JWqflkWi uaYiWoWqflk lb EkZamakZakYa. 
 
   Seak va Ylja ql W pqsZy lb qea uaYiWoWqflk lb EkZamakZakYa fqpaib va
bfkZ W oaWppaoqflk lb mofkYafmiap YlkYaokfkd qea ansWifqy lb jak, qeafo
skWifakWXia ofdeqp, qeWq dltaokjakq fp fkpqfqsqaZ ql paYsoa qelpa
ofdeqp, qeWq fq Zaoftap fqp gspq mlvaoWf bolj qea Ylkpakq lb qea
dltaosaZ, WkZ qea ofdeq lb qea malmia, veak fq XaYljap ZapqosYqfta lb
qelpa akZp, ql Wiqao lo WXlifpe fq WkZ fkpqfqsqa W kav dltaokjakq.  
   Abqao ZaYiWofkd qeWq ilkd apqWXifpeaZ dltaokjakqp pelsiZ klq Xa
YeWkdaZ blo ifdeq WkZ qoWkpfakq YWspap, fq molYaaZp ql WooWfdk qea
cofqfpe dltaokjakq blo W ilkd qoWfk lb WXspap WkZ spsomWqflkp. Sa jWy
dWqeao, bolj qea aksjaoWqflk lb qelpa WXspap, qea bliilvfkd YiWfjp jWZa
Xy qea oatlisqflkfpqp YlkYaokfkd qea ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ fjjskfqfap
lb Yfqfzakp: 
 1. Pea ofdeq lb oamoapakqWqflk fk qea iadfpiWqsoa, W ofdeq fkapqfjWXia
ql qeaj. 
 2. Pea ofdeq ql eWta oamoapakqWqfta XlZfap WppajXiaZ Wq spsWi WkZ
YljbloqWXia miWYap Ylktakfakq ql qea Zamlpfqloy lb qeafo msXifY oaYloZp.
 3. Pea ofdeq ql eWta boansakq pappflkp lb qea iadfpiWqsoa. 
 4. Pea ofdeq ql eWta W pypqaj lb ksqsoWifzWqflk iWvp. 
 5. Pea ofdeq ql eWta Wk fkZamakZakq gsZfYfWoy. 
 6. Pea ofdeq ql lmmlpa W jsiqfqsZa lb lbbfYap. 
 7. Pea ofdeq ql lmmlpa pqWkZfkd Wojfap fs qfja lb maWYa. 
 8. Pea ofdeq ql XWta qea Yftfi mlvao psmaoflo ql qea jfifqWoy mlvao. 
 9. Pea ofdeq ql oapfpq nsWoqaofkd lb WojaZ qollmp Wjlkd qeaj. 
 10. Pea ofdeq ql qoWZa vfqe qea lsqpfZa vloiZ. 
 11. Pea ofdeq ql Wp tlfYa fk qWwWqflk. 
 12. Pea ofdeq ql qofWi Xy W gsoy lb qea tfYfkWda. 
 13. Pea ofdeq lb ElYWi paib-dltaokjakq. 
 
                      Pea BaZaoWi rlkpqfqsqflk. 
 
   Sa eWta WioaWZy paak qeWq Zsofkd qea maoflZ fk vefYe qea OqWqap
Yl-lmaoWqaZ skZao WoqfYiap lb YlkbaZaoWqflk, qea ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ
fjjskfqfap lb qeafo Yfqfzakp vaoa ZaoftaZ awYispftaiy bolj qeafo
oapmaYqfta OqWqap, WkZ qeWq qea mlvao lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap ZfZ klq
awqakZ ql qea Ylkqoli lb qea fkZftfZsWi, pWta fk W bav ifjfqaZ WkZ
pmaYfbfaZ YWpap; WkZ qeWq Wp qeak YlkpqfqsqaZ qea QkfqaZ OqWqap ZfZ klq
Wqqajmq ql doWkq lo dsWoWkqaa ql qea fkZftfZsWi Yfqfzak Wky ofdeqp,
moftfiadap, lo fjjskfqfap, pWta ql Yfqfzakp lb lka OqWqa fk Wklqeao
OqWqa.(7) 
   Seak, smlk qea WZlmqflk lb qea BaZaoWi rlkpqfqsqflk, BaZaoWi mlvao
lmaoWqaZ ZfoaYqiy smlk fkZftfZsWi Yfqfzakp lb qea ifjfqaZ OqWqap, qea
ksjXao lb BaZaoWi dsWoWkqaap lb qeafo ofdeqp vWp awqakZaZ Wipl. Peapa
dsWoWkqaap vaoa qea kaYappWoy YlooaiWqftap lb qea pmaYfbfY mlvaoaop
doWkqaZ ql qea BaZaoWi dltaokjakq, WkZ Woa qea psmoaja iWv lb qea iWkZ
lk qea psXgaYqp ql vefYe qeay oabao. 
   csq fq Xy kl jaWkp bliilvp bolj qefp qeWq qea BaZaoWi dltaokjakq fp
psmoaja YlkYaokfkd Wii qea ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ fjjskfqfap lb qea
Yfqfzak. Kk qea YlkqoWoy, vefia fq fp psmoaja fs fqp pmeaoa WkZ
mlppappap Wjmia Wsqelofqy ql akbloaa qea mlvaop awmoappiy ZaiadWqaZ ql
fq Xy qea rlkpqfqsqflk, fq fp lkiy W dltaokjakq lb ZaiadWqaZ WkZ ifjfqaZ
mlvaop, WkZ qea OqWqap, fk blojfkd fq, awmoappiy oaqWfkaZ WkZ oapaotaZ
fk qeajpaitap qea WXplisqa Ylkqoli, ZfoaYqflk, WkZ pltaoafdkqy ltao
qeafo Yfqfzakp YlkYaokfkd W tWpq oapfZssj lb ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ
fjjskfqfap vefYe, moflo ql qea WZlmqflk lb qea rlkpqfqsqflk, qeay eWZ
oadsiWqaZ awYispftaiy.(8) Blo fkpqWkYa, fq eWp katao Xaak YljqakZaZ qeWq
qea rlkpqfqsqflk, Wp lofdfkWiiy boWjaZ, YoaWqaZ fk qea BaZaoWi
dltaokjakq Wky mlvao ql apqWXifpe Wky YlZa lb jskfYfmWi iWv WmmifYWXia
ql qea OqWqap Yljmlpfkd fq, oadsiWqfta lb Wii moftWqa ofdeqp Xaqvaak jWk
WkZ jWk fk plYfaqy, lo qeWq rlkdoapp jWy spsom qea mlvaop lb OqWqa
iadfpiWqsoap YlkYaokfkd psYe iadfpiWqflk. Pea Osmoaja rlsoq lb qea
QkfqaZ OqWqap eWp oamaWqaZiy qWhak lYYWpflk ql mlfkq lsq qeWq kl psYe
mlvao awfpqp, afqeao skZao qea lofdfkWi rlkpqfqsqflk lo Xy tfoqsa lb Wky
lb qea WjakZjakqp.(9) Ap va peWii paa iWqao, W tWpq Wjlskq lb ifqfdWqflk
vefYe eWp Wofpak skZao qea YlkpqfqsqflkWi WjakZjakqp eWp Xaak XWpaZ smlk
W YlkbspaZ klqflk qeWq qea TEEE, TER, WkZ TR AjakZjakqp fk plja vWy
WiqaoaZ WkZ awqakZaZ qea dakaoWi pYlma lb BaZaoWi mlvaop, atak ql qea
mlfkq lb abbaYqfkd qefp bskZWjakqWi YeWkda. csq Wk skXolhak ifka lb
BaZaoWi ZaYfpflkp eWp ZakfaZ qeWq psYe W YeWkda fk qea lodWkfY pqosYqsoa
lb qea BaZaoWi dltaokjakq vWp afqeao YlkqajmiWqaZ lo abbaYqaZ Xy qea
WjakZjakqp, WkZ mlfkq lsq qeWq qea iadfpiWqflk vefYe rlkdoapp fp
WsqeaofzaZ ql akWYq skZao qea WjakZjakqp fp klq dakaoWi iadfpiWqflk smlk
qea ofdeqp lb Yfqfzakp, Xsq lkiy YaoqWfk YlooaYqfta iadfpiWqflk, fb psYe
Xa kaYappWoy, ql YlskqaoWYq OqWqa iadfpiWqflk molefXfqaZ Xy qea
WjakZjakqp smlk pmaYfWi psXgaYqp kWjaZ fk qea WjakZjakqp.(10) 
   Seak va Ylja ql awWjfka qea jsiqfqsZfklsp ZaYfpflkp lb qea Osmoaja
rlsoq lk nsapqflkp vefYe eWta Wofpak skZao qea WjakZjakqp fq vfii Xa
paak qeWq qea YWpap eWta blo qea jlpq mWoq klq lofdfkWqaZ fk Wky WiiadaZ
WYq lb qea BaZaoWi dltaokjakq fktWZfkd qea pmeaoa lb OqWqa WYqflk, Xsq
smlk qea Ylkqakqflk jWZa Xy Yfqfzakp lb qea OqWqap qeWq BaZaoWi mlvaop,
Wp akiWodaZ Xy qea WjakZjakqp, Woa jsYe jloa bWo-oaWYefkd WkZ
oapqofYqfta smlk OqWqa mlvaop qeWk qea BaZaoWi Ylsoqp qeajpaitap eWta
Xaak vfiifkd ql WZjfq. Pea ZaYfpflkp oakZaoaZ Xy qea Osmoaja rlsoq eWta
fk Wk ltaoveaifsfkd jWglofqy lb YWpap Xaak WdWfkpq qea XolWZ abbaYq lb
qea YlkpqfqsqflkWi WjakZjakqp Wp Wsqelofzfkd awqakZaZ BaZaoWi mlvaop,
lo Wp oapqofYqfkd OqWqa mlvaop, YlkqakZaZ blo Xy qea Yfqfzakp; WkZ qeay
ZaYiWoa skWkfjlspiy qea Ylkqfksfkd mlvao lb qea OqWqap, klqvfqepqWkZfkd
qea WjakZjakqp, ql oadsiWqa awYispftaiy qea ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ
fjjskfqfap lb Yfqfzakp smlk qea jWqqaop fk fppsa, psXgaYq lkiy ql qea
mWoqfYsiWo ifjfqWqflkp kWjaZ fk qea WjakZjakqp.(10) 
   Oaaffkd klv qeWq qea ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ fjjskfqfap lb qea
Yfqfzakp Woa ZamakZakq, blo WYhklviaZdjasq WkZ molqaYqflk, smlk ZsWi
dltaokjakqp, gspq Wp qea WiiadfWkYa lb qea Yfqfzak fp Zsa ql ZsWi
dltaokjakqp, iaq sp kawq YlkpfZao qea pWbadsWoZp WkZ molqaYqflkp lb
qelpa ofdeqp lbbaoaZ ql qea Yfqfzak Xy qea BaZaoWi WkZ OqWqa
dltaokjakqp. AkZ, Wp qea BaZaoWi dltaokjakq, Wiqelsde ifjfqaZ fk fqp
pmeaoa, fp psmoaja, WkZ Wp Wii lqeao ofdeqp, klq ZaoftaZ bolj lo
dsWoWkqaaZ Xy fq, ZamakZ blo qeafo oaYldkfqflk WkZ molqaYqflk smlk qea
OqWqap, qea loZaoiy jaqelZ lb YlkpfZaoWqflk vlsiZ paaj ql Xa, ql fknsfoa
bfopq veWq ofdeqp lb qea Yfqfzak qea BaZaoWi dltaokjakq doWkqp lo
skZaoqWhap ql molqaYq, WkZ veWq fq eWp kafqeao doWkqaZ klo skZaoqWhak
ql dsWoWkqaa. Blo Wii ofdeqp klq pl doWkqaZ lo dsWoWkqaaZ Xy qea BaZaoWi
dltaokjakq Woa ZamakZakq blo qeafo awfpqakYa WkZ qeafo YlkqfksWkYa smlk
qea OqWqa lb vefYe qea fkZftfZsWi fp W Yfqfzak.(11) 
 
            Nfdeqp, Loftfiadap, WkZ Ejjskfqfap CoWkqaZ lo  
           CsWoWkqaaZ ql qea rfqfzak Xy qea QkfqaZ OqWqap. 
 
   Peapa jWy Xa YiWppfbfaZ Wp bliilvp:  
   1. Nfdeqp doWkqaZ lo dsWoWkqaaZ Xy qea rlkpqfqsqflk lb qea QkfqaZ
OqWqap Wp lofdfkWiiy boWjaZ, lo Xy qea bfopq qvaita WjakZjakqp qeaoaql. 
    2. Nfdeqp doWkqaZ lo dsWoWkqaaZ Xy qea TEEE, TER, WkZ TR AjakZjakqp. 
 
    Bfopq, qeak, qea ofdeqp, moftfiadap, lo fjjskfqfap doWkqaZ lo
dsWoWkqaaZ ql qea Yfqfzak Xy qea rlspqfqsqflk lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap Wp
lofdfkWiiy boWjaZ, lo Xy qea bfopq qvaita WjakZjakqp qeaoaql, Woa, fk
qea loZao lb qeafo aksjaoWqflk, lo Xy kaYappWoy fjmifYWqflk, Wp bliilvp:

   1. A ofdeq, PeWq Yfqfzakp lb qea OqWqap Yljmlpfkd qea Qkflk, eWtfkd
qea nsWifbfYWqflkp oansfpfqa blo aiaYqlop lb qea jlpq ksjaolsp XoWkYe
lb qea OqWqa iadfpiWqsoa, peWii mlppapp qea ofdeq WkZ moftfiada lb
aiaYqlop blo jajXaop lb qea Dlspa lb NamoapakqWqftap lb qea QkfqaZ
OqWqap Yelpak ataoy paYlkZ yaWo Xy qea malmia lb qea QkfqaZ Oqsqap.
(Aoq. 1, OaY. 2, ri. 1.)(12) 
   2. A moftfiada. PeWq psYe Yfqfzakp peWii Xa aifdfXia ql jajXaopefm lb
qea Dlspa lb NamoapakqWqftap, fb qeay mlppapp YaoqWfk nsWifbfYWqflkp lb
Wda, iakdqe lb Yfqfzakpefm, WkZ Woa fkeWXfqWkqp lb qea OqWqa bolj vefYe
qeay Woa Yelpak. (AoH 1, OaY. 2, ri. 2.)   3. A ofdeq. PeWq
