WkZ dWja fk ataoy OqWqa Xailkd ql, maYsifWoiy WkZ lb ofdeq, WkZ bloj
mWoq lb qea bllZ psmmiy lb, qea malmia fk aWYe OqWqa, WkZ qeWq fq fp
vfqefk qea mlifYa mlvaop lb qea OqWqa, vfqelsq Wky ofdeq lb fkqaobaoakYa
Xy BaZaoWi Wsqelofqy, ql Zaqaojfka vel peWii WkZ vel peWii klq qWha qea
bfpe WkZ dWja vfqefk eao XloZaop, WkZ atak ql molefXfq qea pefmmfkd lb
qea pWja XaylsZ qea ifjfqp lb qea OqWqa. Pesp veak W RfodfkfW iWv
mskfpeaZ W Yfqfzak lb IWoyiWkZ blo qWhfkd lypqaop bolj RfodfkfW lypqao
XaZp, WkZ ea YiWfjaZ qeWq ea vWp akdWdaZ fk YljjaoYa, qea Osmoaja rlsoq
pspqWffkaZ qea OqWqa iWv, WkZ ZakfaZ qea YiWfj lb ifYakpa ql bfpe fk
RfodfkfW vWqaop Wp W jWqqao lb YljjaoYfWi ofdeq.(78) Ol, W iWv lb
rlkkaYqfYsq oadsiWqfkd qea jWkkao lb qWhfkd dWja fk qeWq OqWqa WkZ
bloXfZZfkd fqp awmloqWqflk vWp eaiZ tWifZ.(79) Pea Zsqy lb moapaotfkd
qea dWja vWp ZaYiWoaZ ql Xa W qospq blo eao lvk malmia. AkZ OqWqa iWvp
molefXfqfkd aweWspqfta jaqelZp lb bfpefkd fk vWqaop vfqefk OqWqa
gsofpZfYqflk, lo qea spa lb ZapqosYqfta fkpqosjakqp, Woa vfqefk qea
mlvaop lb qea OqWqa.(80) 
 
        Pea Nfdeq lb qea rfqfzak ql qea Sofq lb DWXaWp rlomsp 
                           (Nfdeq 23 WXlta) 
 
   ciWYhpqlka YWiip qea vofq lb XWXaWp Ylomsp "qea jlpq YaiaXoWqaZ vofq
fk qea xkdifpe iWv,"(81) WkZ ea oabaop ql qea osfklsp DWXaWp rlomsp AYq
lb xkdiWkZ, 31 reWoiap EE, Y. 2, Wp "boansakqiy YlkpfZaoaZ Wp Wklqeao
IWdkW reWoqW." 
   Pea Osmoaja rlsoq lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap eWp YeWoWYqaofzaZ fq: "Pea
doaWq vofq lb eWXasp Ylomsp eWp Xaak blo Yakqsofap apqaajaZ qea Xapq WkZ
lkiy psbbfYfakq Zabakpa lb maoplkWi boaaZlj. Ek xkdiWkZ, Wbqao W ilkd
pqosddia, fq vWp bfojiy dsWoWkqaaZ Xy qea bWjlsp DWXaWqf rlomsp AYq lb
IWy 27, 1679. - - Eq vWp Xolsdeq ql AjaofYW Xy qea Ylilkfpqp WkZ YiWfjaZ
Wp Wjlkd qea fjjajlofWi ofdeqp ZapYakZaZ ql qeaj bolj qeafo
WkYapqlop.(82) Kb qefp vofq fq jWy Xa pWfZ qosiy qeWq fq XWp aifYfqaZ
jloa akYljfsjp bolj XakYe WkZ XWo qeWk Wky lqeao fk qea Xllh, WkZ qeWq
ZfpYsppflk lb fq paajp ql Wolspa veWqatao lb ailnsakYa gsZdap WkZ
WZtlYWqap jWy mlppapp. 
   Ek bloj fq fp W vofq ajWkWqfkd bolj qea gsZfYfWi plsoYa fkqospqaZ vfqe
fqp haamfkd WkZ fppsWkYa, ZfoaYqaZ ql qea YspqlZfWk lb Wky maoplk
ZaqWfkaZ lk W YofjfkWi lo W Yftfi YeWoda, ZfoaYqfkd efj ql molZsYa qea
XlZy lb qea maoplk fk YspqlZy Wq W qfja WkZ miWYa ZapfdkWqaZ fk qea
