psXjfq ql WkZ oaYafta veWqatao gsZdjakq qea gsZda lo Ylsoq WvWoZfkd qea
vofq peWii YlkpfZao fk qeWq XaeWib. Pea kWja lb qea vofq lofdfkWqaZ fk
qea bWYq qeWq Wq qea qfja fq YWja fkql spa Wii vofqp fk xkdiWkZ vaoa
vofqqak fk HWqfk, WkZ qefp mWoqfYsiWo vofq ZfoaYqaZ qea YspqlZfWk lb qea
mofplkao "eWXaWp Ylomsp," "qels peWiq eWta qea XlZy" lb pl WkZ pl, Wq
psYe WkZ psYe qfja WkZ miWYa. 
   Eq fp klq vfqefk qea msomlpa lb qefp vloh ql aiWXloWqa qea Zfbbaoakq
hfkZp lb vofqp lb eWXaWp Ylomsp WsZ qea Zfbbaoakq msomlpap blo vefYe
qeay Woa fktlhaZ. PeWq jWy Xa paak Xy oabaoakYa ql qea Wsqelofqfap
nslqaZ. Peaoa vaoa vofqp lb eWXaWp Ylomsp WZ oapmlkZakZsj, lo ql akWXia
qea mWoqy Wmmiyfkd blo qea vofq ql lXqWfk Wk Wkpvao lb plja ploq bolj
qea mWoqy fk YspqlZy; WkZ vofqp WZ pWqfpbWYfakZsj, lo ql pWqfpby W
gsZdjakq lo lqeao ZajWkZ, vefYe vofq Zlap klq awfpq vfqe sp; lo WZ
molpadsakZj, WZ qapqfbfYWkZsj, WZ ZaifXaoWkZsj, ql molpaYsqa pljaqefkd,
ql qapqfby WXlsq pljaqefkd, ql ZaifXaoWqa WXlsq pljaqefkd. Eq fp W
Yljjlk qefkd, blo awWjmia, veaoa W mofplkao YlkbfkaZ fk gWfi lo
makfqakqfWoy fp W kaYYappWoy vfqkapp Wq W qofWi, ql eWta efj molZsYaZ
