gsZda lo lqeao Wsqelofqy. 
   csq qea Yljjlk vofq qea lka YeaofpeaZ Wp klka lqeao, fp qea vofq lb
eWXaWp Ylomsp WZ psXgfYfakZsj aq oaYfmfakZsj, YljsWWkZfkd qea YspqlZfWk
