gsofpmosZakYa. 
 
   Kb qea Ejjskfqy lb qea rfqfzak AdWfkpq cfiip lb AqqWfkZao WkZ xw
   Llpq BWYql HWvp. (Ejjskffqy 24 WXlta). 
 
   Pefp fjjskfqy fp dsWoWkqaaZ, Xlqe Wp WdWfkpq qea JWqflk WkZ qea OqWqa
(Aoq. 1, OaY. 9, ri. 3, WkZ Aoq. E, Oaa. 10, ai. 1.)(87) 
   A Xfii lb WqqWfkZao fp W iadfpiWqfta WYq vefYe fkbifYqp mskfpejWakqp
vfqelsq W gsZfYfWi qofWi.(88) OsYe Xfiip vaoa, fk xkdiWkZ, pljaqfjap
