skZao qea aya lb qea Osmoaja rlsoq. AkZ lb qea oaWplkp iaWZfkd ql qea
WZlmqflk lb qelpa YiWspap lb qea rlkpqfqsqflk bloXfZZfkd psYe
iadfpiWqflk afqeao Xy qea JWqflk lo qea OqWqa, ea pWfZ: "SeWqatao
oapmaYq jfdeq eWta Xaak baiq blo qea OqWqa pltaoafdkqfap, fq fp klq ql
Xa ZfpdsfpaZ qeWq qea boWjaop lb qea rlkpqfqsqflk tfavaZ vfqe plja
