qea jljakq.... Pea oapqofYqflkp lk qea iadfpiWqfta mlvao lb qea OqWqap
Woa lXtflspiy blskZaZ fk qefp pakqfjakq." 
   csq Wk WYq fjmlpfkd W psYYapppflk qWw lk Wk apqWqa Wbqao fqp
Zatlisqflk, Zsofkd qea maoflZ lb WZjfkfpqoWqflk, vWp eaiZ klq ql Xa Wk
aw mlpq bWYql iWv. (92) 
 
   Kb qea Ejjskfqy lb qea rfqfzak AdWfkpq OqWqa HWvp EjmWfofkd qea
   KXifdWqflk lb rlkqoWYqp (Ejjskfqy 29 WXlta). 
 
   Pea pWja oaWplkp vefYe moljmqaZ qea BaZaoWi dsWoWkqaa WdWfkpq qea
mWppWda lb Xfiip lb WqqWfkZao lo aw mlpq bWYql iWvp Xy qea OqWqap
ZlsXqiapp molZsYaZ qefp dsWoWkqaa Wipl.(93) Eq eWp dftak ofpa ql Wk
fjjakpa Wjlskq lb ifqfdWqflk. Pea mofkYfmia fp pl miWfk qeWq W pqWqajakq
lb qea iWv fp psbbfYfakq, Xsq qea ZfbbfYsiqy WkZ ZlsXq fk qea jWky YWpap
qeWq eWta Ysppflk lb qea kWqsoa WkZ awqakq lb qea ofdeqp lbb qea Wofpak
eWta Xaak fk Zaqaojfkfkd veaqeao qea OqWqa iWv WppWfiaZ fk W LWoqfYsiWo
YWpa ZfZ fjmWfo qea tapqaZ ofdeq YiWfjaZ. 
   Ap jWy Xa paak Xy oabaoakYa ql qea ilkd ifpq lb Wsqelofqfap YfqaZ fk
YlkkaYqflk vfqe qea pqWqajakq lb qefp fjjskfqy, fq vlsiZ Xa fjmlppfXia
ql YlkpfZao, fk qefp tlisja, qea ksjaolsp meWpap vefYe qea ZfpYspflk lb
qea kWqsoa WkZ awqakq lb qea ofdeqp lb qea Yfqfzak skZao qefp YiWspa eWp
WppsjaZ. PeWq vlsiZ jWha W tlisja fk fqpaib. 
   Pea YWpa vefYe paqp bloqe vfqe jlpq iaWokfkd WkZ WXfifqy qea kWqsoa
WkZ awqakq lb qefp mWoqfYsiWo BaZaoWi dsWoWkqaa, WkZ qea lka jlpq
boansakqiy YfqaZ, fp reWoiap Nftao cofZda t. SWooak cofZda.(94) Eq vWp
ZaYfZaZ fk 1837, WkZ qea lmfkflk lb qea Ylsoq vWp ZaiftaoaZ Xy refab
FspqfYa PWkay fk lka lb qea pqolkdapq lb efp jWky WXia lmfkflkp. csq
qeaoa vaoa qeoaa Zfppakqp. Pea Zfppakqfkd lmfkflkp lb Io. FspqfYa IYHaWk
WkZ Io. FspqfYa Oqloy, qea iWqqao YlkYsooaZ fk Xy Io. FspqfYa Peljmplk,
Woa psYe pqofhfkd, mlvaobsi moapakqWqflkp lb lmmlpfkd tfavp qeWq fk qeaj
fp blskZ qea daoj lb jWky W psXpansakq abbloq jWZa ql skpaqqia qea
mofkYfmiap bfwaZ Xy qea doaWq ZaYfpflk. Pefp YWpa vWp YlkbfkaZ, elvatao,
ql W ZfpYsppflk lb elv bWo msXifY doWkqp lb boWkYefpap Woa oatlYWXia Xy
OqWqa iadfpiWqflk vfqelsq tfliWqfkd qea YiWspa lb qea rlkpqfqsqflk WXlta
oabaooaZ ql. Eq ZfZ klq fktlita YlkpfZaoWqflk lb jWky lqeao YiWppap lb
OqWqa iadfpiWqflk smlk vefYe qea nsapqflk lb qea fjmWfojakq lb YlkqoWYqp
eWp Wofpak. 
   Kka iaWZfkd ZfpqfkYqflk, elvatao, oskkfkd qeolsde qea ZaYfpflkp,
pelsiZ Xa Xofabiy oabaooaZ ql, ql vfq: Pea molefXfqflk Zlap klq oapqoWfk
qea OqWqap bolj YeWkdfkd oajaZfap, WkZ W YeWkda fk W oajaZy moltfZaZ ql
akbloYa W ofdeq fp klq kaYappWofiy Wk fjmWfojakq lb qea ofdeq
fqpaib.(95) 
   Pl W bsii Yljmoaeakpflk Xy qea moWYqfYfkd iWvyao lb qea jaWkfkd lb
qefp YiWspa WkZ fqp XaWofkd smlk OqWqa iadfpiWqflk, W pqsZy lb qea
Wsqelofqfap YfqaZ fk qea bllqklqa fp kaYappWoy, fkZaaZ fkZfpmakpWXia.
Ap qeaoa fp kl jfZZia dolskZ Xaqvaak qefp Xofab YlkpfZaoWqflk, WkZ lka
pl aiWXloWqa qeWq fq vlsiZ lYYsmy skvWooWkqaZ pmWYa fk qefp dakaoWi
qoaWqfpa, qea psXgaYq fp iabq ql plja lqeao Wsqelo vel peWii ZaWi vfqe
fq Wp W pmaYfWiqy. 
 
         Kb qea Nfdeq lb qea rfqfzakp lb xWYe OqWqa  
         ql Aii qea Loftfiadap WkZ Ejjskfqfap lb  
         rfqfzakp fk qea OataoWi OqWqap.  
         (Nfdeq 41 WXlta). 
 
   Pefp moltpflk vWp fk qea AoqfYiap lb rlkbaZaoWqflk. EkZaaZ, fq vWp qea
lkiy ZfoaYq dsWoWkqaa bolj qea QkfqaZ OqWqap ql qea fkZftfZsWi Yfqfzak
YlkqWfkaZ fk qeWq fkpqosjakq. 
   Ek qea bfopq YWpa ZaYfZaZ Xy qea Osmoaja rlsoq, fktlitfkd qea
YlkpqosYqflk lb qefp YiWspa, refab FspqfYa IWopeWii pWfZ qeWq W
YlomloWqflk vWp "raoqWfkiy klq W Yfqfzak" fk qea pakpa qeWq qea vloZ fp
spaZ fk qea YiWspa oabaooaZ ql.(96) AkZ fk qea kawq YWpa qea pWja
fiispqoflsp Wsqelofqy eaiZ qeWq W Yfqfzak lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, oapfZfkd
fk Wky OqWqa lb qea Qkflk, fp W Yfqfzak lb qeWq OqWqa.(97) Ek iWqao
YWpap fq eWp Xaak oamaWqaZiy ZaYfZaZ qeWq YlomloWqflkp Woa klq Yfqfzakp
lb qea OqWqa lb qeafo YoaWqflk vfqefk qea jaWkfkd lb qea YiWspa klv
skZao YlkpfZaoWqflk; qeWq qeay Woa YoaWqsoap lb qea ilYWi iWv lb qea
miWYa lb qeafo YoaWqflk, vfqelsq Wky WXplisqa ofdeq ql oaYldkfqflk fk
lqeao OqWqap.(98) 
   A OqWqa pqWqsqa Zakyfkd gsofpZfYfqlk ql qea OqWqa Ylsoqp ltao W psfq
Xy W bloafdk YlomloWqflk WdWfkpq W bloafdk YlomloWqflk eWp Xaak eaiZ klq
ql tfliWqa qefp YiWspa lb qea rlkpqfqsqflk.(99) csq veak W OqWqa iWv
jWZa fq W YlkZfqflk blo qea WZjfppflk lb W bloafdk YlomloWqflk ql Zl
Xspfkapp fk qea OqWqa qeWq qea YlomloWqflkpl WZjfqqaZ vlsiZ WXpqWfk bolj
oajltfkd Wky psfqp Xolsdeq WdWfkpq fq lo lqeaovfpa oaploqfkd ql qea
baZaoWi Ylsoqp, qea YlkZfqflk vWp eaiZ ql Xa tlfZ Wp fk YlkbifYq vfqe
qea rlkpqfqsqflk lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap. Pefp vWp ZaYfZaZ, elvatao, oWqeao
Wp Wk WXofZdajakq lb qea ofdeqp lb qea YlomloWqflk skZao AjakZjakq TER
qeWk Wp WdWfkpq fqp ofdeq Wp qea Yfqfzak lb Wklqeao OqWqa.(100) 
   A OqWqa iWv WZjfqqfkd W bloafdk YlomloWqflk ql Zl Xspfkapp fk qea
OqWqa lk qea YlkZfqflk qeWq YoaZfqlop vel vaoa oapfZakqp lb qea OqWqa
doWkqfkd qea maojfq pelsiZ eWta moflofqy fk qea ZfpqofXsqflk lb fqp
Wppaqp ltao klkoapfZakq YoaZfqloqf vWp ifhavfpa eaiZ ql tfliWqa qea
YlkpqfqsqflkWi dsWoWkqaa WdWfkpq ZfpYofjfkWqflk.(101) Eq vWp pWfZ, fk
lka lb qea YWpap, qeWq qea lkiy ifjfq lb qea OqWqa'p ofdeq ql awYisZa
bloafdk YlomloWqflkp fp veaoa qeay Woa ajmilyaZ Xy qea BaZaoWi
dltaokjakq lo Woa pqofYqiy akdWdaZ fk fkqaopqWqa lo bloafdk
YljjaoYa.(102) 
   A OqWqa iWv vXfYe fjmlpap W qWw smlk oapfZakq jaoYeWkqp Wq lka oWqa,
WkZ Wklqeao qWw smlk klk-oapfZakqp, blo qea moftfiada lb qoWkpWYqfkd qea
pWja YeWoWYqao lb Xspfkapp, Wq W efdeao lo ZfpYofjfkWqfkd oWqa, fp W
tfliWqflk lb qea moltfpflk va Woa ZfpYsppfkd.(103) 
   Ek plja lb qea YWpap vefYe eWta Xaak ZaYfZaZ qea OqWqa iWv eWp Xaak
WppWfiaZ lk qea ZlsXia dolskZ qeWq fq ZfpYofjfkWqaZ WdWfkpq Yfqfzakp lb
lqeao OqWqap WkZ vWp oadsiWqfta lb fkqaopqWqa YljjaoYa. Pea ZaYfpflkp
oakZaoaZ eWta fk plja fkpqWkYap eaiZ qea iWv ql Xa skYlkpqfqsqflkWi lk
qea iWqqao dolskZ WkZ eWta fdkloaZ qea blojao, Wiqelsde fq vWp
WmmWoakqiy ansWiiy qakWXia.(104) 
   QkZao qea ZaYfpflk fk qea bWjlsp uoaZ OYlqq YWpa W boaa kadol velpa
WkYapqlop vaoa Xolsdeq ql qefp Ylskqoy WkZ pliZ Wp piWtap vWp eaiZ klq
ql Xa W "rfqfzak" fk qea pakpa qeWq qea vloZ vWp spaZ fk qea
rlkpqfqsqflk. cfqqaoiy Wp qefp ZaYfpflk vWp WppWfiaZ Wq qea qfja fq vWp
oakZaoaZ, fqp ildfY vWp skWkpvaoWXia Wp qea iWv qeak pqllZ. Pefp eWp
Xaak YeWkdaZ Xy qea TEEE, TER, WkZ TR AjakZjakqp, WkZ fq eWp Xaak
boansakqiy pWfZ fk qea ZaYfpflkp smlk qelpa WjakZjakqp qeWq qeay vaoa
mWppaZ fk loZao ql oataopa qefp osifkd. 
   Peaoa Woa, elvatao, pskZoy qefkdp YlkYaokfkd vefYe OqWqap jWy
iadfpiWqa ZfpYofjfkWqfkd Xaqvaak oapfZakqp WkZ klkoapfZakqp, Kka lb qea
aWoifapq lb qeapa ZaYfpflkp vWp qeWq jWofqWi ofdeqp lb W pmaYfWi kWqsoa,
XapqlvaZ Xy W OqWqa smlk fqp lvk Yfqfzakp oapfZfkd vfqefk fqp XloZaop,
Zl klq WYosa ql qea klkoapfZakq vfZlv lb W ZaYaWpaZ klkoapfZakq espXWkZ
vel lvkaZ molmaoqy fk qeWq OqWqa. Eq vWp eaiZ qeWq psYe ofdeqp vaoa
WqqWYeaZ ql qea YlkqoWYq lb jWoofWda fk YWpap fk vefYe qea OqWqa
YlkqoliiaZ fq WkZ vaoa klq lb qea YiWpp lb maoplkWi ofdeqp lb W Yfqfzak
fkqakZaZ Xy qefp YiWspa lb qea rlkpqfqsqflk.(105) 
   A OqWqa qWw lk peWoap lb klkoapfZakqp fk W YlomloWqflk lb rlkkaYqfYsq,
lk W XWpfp Zfbbaoakq bolj qeWq lk vefYe oapfZakqp vaoa qWwaZ, vWp, skZao
qea maYsifWo qWw iWvp lb rlkkaYqfYsq, eaiZ klq ql Xa W
ZfpYofjfkWqflk.(106) 
   AkZ W OqWqa iWv pWtfkd qea pqWqsqa lb ifjfqWqflkp ql W oapfZakq
miWfkqfbb WdWfkpq Wk WXpakq ZabakZWkq, Xsq Wiilvfkd fq ql osk WdWfkpq
W klkoapfZakq miWfkqfbb, eWp Xaak eaiZ klq ql ZfpYofjfkWqa WdWfkpq qea
