WkZ Yljbloq lb qea malmia.(108) A iWv lb qea OqWqa lb ElvW jWhfkd
maoplkp ifWXia blo Wky ZWjWdap WYYosfkd bolj qeafo Wiilvfkd YWqqia bolj
PawWp ql osk Wq iWoda WkZ pmoaWZ W ZfpaWpa hklvk Wp PawWp batao vWp eaiZ
ql vloh kl ZfpYofjfkWqflk, WkZ ql Xa vfqefk qea mlifYa mlvaop lb qea
OqWqap.(109) A pfjfiWo iWv WdWfkpq fkqolZsYfkd ZfpaWpaZ ifta pqlYh fkql
rliloWZl vWp smeaiZ.(110) Ek qea YWpa lb NWpjsppak t. EZWel,(111) qea
