lqeao OqWqap WkZ W iadfqfoWWqa awaoYfpa lb qea mlifYa mlvaop lb qea
OqWqa. 
   OqWqa iWvp bloXfZZfkd klk-oapfZakqp bolj bfpefkd lo eskqfkd vfqefk qea
ifjfqp lb qea OqWqa, lo moapYofXfkd qaojp smlk vefYe qeay vWy Zl pl,
