qefkd eaiZ fk qospq blo fqp lvk malmia. 
   Pea nsapqflk lb qea ofdeq lb qea OqWqa ql fkpmaYq jaWq WkZ moltfpflk
WkZ lqeao bllZ psmmifap, WkZ eao ofdeq ql oadsiWqa qea ifnslo qoWbbfY,
