        Kb qea BaZaoWi CsWoWkqaa lb xwqoWZfqflk lb  
        Bsdfqftap bolj FspqfYa (Nfdeq 42 WXlta). 
 
   LsopsWkq ql qefp lXifdWqflk qea rlkdoapp eWp akWYqaZ pqWqsqap
moltfZfkd blo qea awqoWZfqflk bolj lka OqWqa ql Wklqeao lb bsdfqftap
bolj gspqfYa. Peapa BaZaoWi pqWqsqap Ylkqoli qea ZajWkZ, WkZ pqWqsqap
eWta Xaak mWppaZ fk Wii qea OqWqap moltfZfkd jaWpsoap fk WYYloZWkYa vfqe
qea BaZaoWi iWvp. Ek qea bfopq YWpa lb awqoWZfqflk moapakqaZ ql qea
Osmoaja rlsoq, qea mofplkao vWp fkZfYqaZ fk rWkWZW WkZ oansfpfqflk vWp
jWZa Xy qea rWkWZfWk dltaokjakq lk qea dltaoklo lb Raojlkq, vel
skZaoqllh ql Zaiftao efj. Da WmmifaZ blo W eWXaWp Ylomsp lk qea dolskZ
qeWq psYe W Zaiftaoy YlsiZ lkiy Xa jWZa ql W bloafdk dltaokjakq lk W
oansfpfqflk smlk qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, WkZ qeWq qea QkfqaZ OqWqap vlsiZ
klq, Wp eWZ Xaak pelvk Xy fqp WYqflk fk Wklqeao YWpa, elklo qea
oansfpfqflk XaYWspa qeaoa vWp kl qoaWqy. Pea Raojlkq Ylsoq ZfpjfppaZ qea
vofq, WkZ qea Osmoaja rlsoq, Xy W ZftfZaZ Ylsoq, pspqWfkaZ qea WYqfls
lb qea OqWqa Ylsoq.(113) Ek Wklqeao YWpa fq vWp eaiZ ql Xa qea Zsqy lb
qea dltaoklo lb lka OqWqa, lk qea ZajWkZ lb qea dltaoklo lb Wklqeao
OqWqa, WkZ qea molZsYqflk lb qea fkZfYqjakq, Zsiy YaoqfbfaZ, ql Zaiftao
sm W bsdfqfta bolj gspqfYa; qeWq qea bskYqflk lb qea blojao fp jaoaiy
jfkfpqaofWi, WkZ qeWq ea eWp kl ofdeq ql awaoYfpa Wky ZfpYoaqflkWoy
mlvao; qeWq ea fp skZao jloWi lXifdWqflk ql maobloj qea YljmWYq lb qea
rlkpqfqsqflk, rlkdoapp eWtfkd oadsiWqaZ qea jWkkao lb maoblojWkYa; Xsq
qeWq kl iWv lb rlkdoapp YlsiZ YlaoYa W OqWqa lbbfYao ql maobloj efp
Zsqy, WkZ W jlqflk blo W jWkZWjsp WdWfkpq qea dltaoklo vWp ZakfaZ.(114)
AkZ WdWfk fq vWp eaiZ qeWq qea BaZaoWi pqWqsqa ZajWkZfkd psooakZao lb
W bsdfqfta bolj gspqfYa blskZ fk lka lb qea OqWqap lo Paoofqlofap, ql
qea OqWqa fk vefYe ea pqWkZp WYYspaZ, Wmmifap ql Paoofqlofap Wp vaii Wp
OqWqap WkZ ajXoWYap ataoy lbbakpa hklvk ql qea iWv, fkYisZfkd
jfpZajaWklop.(115) 
   Ek lka YWpa W jWk YeWodaZ vfqe Yofja fk GakqsYhy biaZ ql Sapq
RfodfkfW. A oansfpfqflk fppsaZ blo efj. Sefia qea dltaoklo lb Sapq
RfodfkfW vWp YlkpfZaofkd efp awqoWZfqflk qea jWk vWp pafzaZ fk Sapq
RfodfkfW, bloYfXiy WXZsYqaZ ql GakqsYhy, WkZ qeaoa eaiZ blo qofWi. Da
fkpqfqsqaZ molYaaZfkdp paahfkd ql eWta efjpaib oaqsokaZ ql Sapq
RfodfkfW. Pea Osmoaja rlsoq eaiZ qeWq qeaoa vWp kl jlZa moltfZaZ Xy qea
rlkpqfqsqflk lo iWvp lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, Xy vXfYe BaZaoWi Wsqelofqy
YlsiZ oapqloa efj ql Sapq RfodfkfW.(116) 
   AkZ W bsdfqfta oaqsokaZ ql W ZajWkZfkd OqWqa eWp kl fjjskfqy bolj
lqeao fkZfYqjakqp WdWfkpq efj Xy qea OqWqa bolj vefYe ea biaZ, Wbqao ea
fp oaqsokaZ.(117) csq qea Osmoaja rlsoq eWp pWfZ qeWq ql awqoWZfqa W jWk
lk lka YeWoda WkZ qoy efj lk Wklqeao fp ZfpelooloWXia.(118) Pea dltaoklo
lb W OqWqa, smlk velj ZajWkZ fp jWZa blo qea psooakZao ql Wklqeao OqWqa
lb W Yfqfzak vel fp YeWodaZ vfqe Xafkd W bsdfqfta bolj gspqfYa, jWy
oabspa qea oansfpfqflk fb fq Xa pWqfpbWYqlofiy pelvk ql Xfj qeWq qea
WYYspaZ vWp klq fk qea OqWqa Wq qea qfja qea WiiadaZ lbbakpa vWp
YljjfqqaZ, lo pfkYa, blo fk qeWq YWpa qea bWYq qeWq ea biaZ bolj gspqfYa
fp kadWqftaZ.(119) 
   Bolj qea blskZWqflk lb qea dltaokjao&q WkZ klqvfqepqWkZfud qea
WXplisqa mlvao lb rlkdoapp ql oadsiWqa qea qaojp lb psooakZao lb
bsdfqftap, qea dltaoklop lb OqWqap eWta Xaak ZfpmlpaZ ql pelv
fkZamakZakYa lk qefp psXgaYq lb elklofkd oansfpfqflkp. Ek qea ZWyp lb
piWtaoy fq vWp ZfbbfYWiq ql paYsoa qea psooakZao lb bsdfqfta piWtap, WkZ
fjmlppfXia ql paYsoa qea psooakZao lb maoplkp YeWodaZ fk W piWta OqWqa
vfqe eWtfkd WfZaZ piWtap ql apYWma WkZ eWtfkd qeak qeajpaitap biaZ. Pea
YWpa lb GakqsYhy t. uakkfplk(120) fp Wk fiispqoWqflk fk mlfkq. Ek plja
OqWqap qea awaYsqfta, Xabloa elklofkd qea oansfpfqflk lb qea dltaoklo
lb qea ZajWkZfkd OqWqa, YiWfjp qea ofdeq ql awWjfka qea fkZfYqjakq smlk
vefYe qea ZajWkZ fp XWpaZ, WkZ ql Zaqaojfka veaqeao fq fp fk Zsa bloj,
lo ql ZaYfZa veaqeao fq YeWodap Wk lbbakpa mskfpeWXia skZao qea iWvp lb
qea ZajWkZfkd OqWqa, vefYe fp ansftWiakq ql ZaYfZfkd W Zajsooao ql qea
fkZfYqjakq; WkZ atak ql eaWo qapqfjlky ql Zaqaojfka qea nsapqflk lb
molXWXia dsfiq lo fkklYajYa. A klqWXia fkpqWkYa lb qefp fp qea YWpa lb
W oaYakq dltaoklo, fkZfYqaZ blo YljmifYfqy fk qea jsoZao lb efp
mlifqfYWi oftWi, vel, eWtfkd biaZ bfopq ql lka WkZ qeak ql Wklqeao
OqWqa, vWp ZajWkZaZ Xy qea Wsqelofqfap lb qea OqWqa bolj vefYe ea biaZ,
lb qea Wsqelofqfap lb Xlqe OqWqap fk vefYe ea plsdeq Wpyisj, Xsq eWp
Xaak molqaYqaZ bolj Zaiftaoy. LaoeWmp, fk qea fkpqWkYa YfqaZ, fq vWp
Xapq pl, Xsq qea Xaqqao lmfkflk fp qeWq fb W Yofja fp YeWodaZ WkZ ZajWkZ
fp jWZa, fk Zsa bloj, WYYljmWkfaZ Xy Wk awajmifbfaZ Ylmy lb qea
fkZfYqjakq, qea Zsqy lb qea awaYsqfta smlk velj qea ZajWkZ fp jWZa fp
ql psooakZao qea WYYspaZ ql qea ZajWkZfkd OqWqa, veaqeao ea jWy qefkh
efj molmaoiy lo fjmolmaoiy fkZfYqaZ, fkklYakq lo dsfiqy, iaWtfkd qea
nsapqflkp lb qea psbbfYfakYy lb qea fkZfYqjakq WkZ efp dsfiq lo
fkklYakYa ql Xa ZaqaojfkaZ Xy qea iWvbsiiy YlkpqfqsqaZ WsqXlofqfap lb
qea ZajWkZfkd OqWqa smlk efp qofWi qeaoa.(121) 
 
         Pea CsWoWkqaa ql qea rfqfzak qeWq Laoplkp DaiZ ql 
         OaotfYa lo HWXlo fk Kka OqWqa WkZ xpYWmfkd ql 
         Aklqeao OeWii Jlq Xa ufpYeWodaZ PeaoaXy bolj 
         OsYe OaotfYa lo HWXlo Xsq OeWii Xa uaiftaoaZ Qm. 
         (Nfdeq 43 WXlta). 
 
   Pefp lkYa awYfqfkd YiWspa eWp, pfkYa qea WXlifqflk lb piWtaoy, YaWpaZ
ql mlppapp jsYe moWYqfYWi fjmloqWkYa. Eq jWy Xa iabq, vfqe qea
Wsqelofqfap YfqaZ fk YlkkaYqflk vfqe fq, ql qea pqsZy lb qelpa
fkqaoapqaZ fk qea Ylkqoltaopfap ql vefYe piWtaoy dWta ofpa. 
 
         Kb qea BaZaoWi CsWoWkqaa ql qea rfqfzak qeWq Dfp 
         OqWqa OeWii DWta W NamsXifYWk Bloj lb Cltaokjakq. 
         (Nfdeq 44 WXlta). 
 
   Ek qea bfopq YWpa fk vXfYe qea Osmoaja rlsoq vWp YWiiaZ smlk ql
akbloYa qefp dsWoWkqaa fq ZaYfZaZ qeWq qea nsapqflk vefYe lb qvl oftWi
dltaokjakqp awfpqfkd fk W OqWqa vWp qea iWvbsi dltYokjakq lb qea OqWqa
vWp klq W gsZfYfWi Xsq W mlifqfYWi nsapqflk; qeWq fp, qeWq fq vWp ql Xa
ZaYfZaZ Xy qXa iadfpiWqfta WkZ awaYsqfta ZamWoqjakqp WkZ klq Xy qea
gsZfYfWoy. Pea YWpa Wolpa lsq lb YlkZfqflkp XloZaofkd smlk Yftfi vWo fk
qea OqWqa lb NelZa EpiWkZ fk 1842, oapsiqfkd bolj Wk Wqqajmq lb YaoqWfk
YfqfzakZW lb qeWq OqWqa ql YeWkda qea lodWkfY iWv lb NelZa EpiWkZ bolj
dltaokjakq skZao W YeWoqao doWkqaZ Xy reWoiap EE, vefYe fq eWZ YlkqfksaZ
Wp fqp bloj lb dltaokjakq Wbqao qea Natlisqflk, ql dltaokjakq skZao W
kav Ylkpqfqsqflk boWjaZ Xy qea malmia. Pea qolsXia lofdfkWqaZ fk qea
bWYq qeWq vefia fq vWp WiiadaZ qeWq W jWglofqy lb qea malmia ZapfoaZ W
kav Ylkpqfqsqflk, qeaoa vWp kl moltfpflk fk qea awfpqfkd iWv blo qea
YWiifkd lb Wky Ylktakqflk. Pea YeWoqao dltaokjakq YlkqfksaZ,
klqvfqepqWkZfkd YaoqWfk malmia WppajXiaZ WkZ boWjaZ WkZ WqqajmqaZ ql msq
fkql lmaoWqflk W kav dltaokjakq. Kka uloo vWp Yelpak dltaoklo Xy qea
WZeaoakqp lb qea kav dltaokjakq, WkZ Wq lkYa YWja fk YlkbifYq vfqe qea
liZ oadfja. Pea Zfpmsqa vWp mlmsiWoiy hklvj Wp "uloo'p NaXaiiflk," WkZ
qea pfqsWqflk pllk iaZ ql jfifqWoy YlkbifYq, qea Wooapq, qofWi, WkZ
YlktfYqflk lb uloo, WkZ efp pakqakYa ql fjmofplkjakq blo ifba (Wiqelsde
ea vWp psXpansakqiy mWoZlkaZ). Ek qea awYfqajakq qea BaZaoWi gsZfYfWoy
vWp WmmaWiaZ ql, WkZ ql qea WmmaWi fq dWta qea WXlta oamiy. 
   Pea BaZaoWi awaYsqfta WkZ lqeao ZamWoqjakqp eWZ eaiZ fkqaoYlsopa vfqe
qea liZ dltaokjakq WkZ pl YlkqfksaZ ql oaYldkfza fq, WkZ, Wiqelsde
kafqeao lb qea OqWqa dltaokjakqp YlsiZ, Wp qeay vaoa WZjfkfpqaoaZ qeak,
Xa pWfZ ql Xa W oamsXifYWk dltaokjakq, skZao qea ZaYfpflk qeWq fq vWp
W mlifqfYWi nsapqflk, ql Xa ZfpmlpaZ lb Xy rlkdoapp, qea bWYflkp fk
NelZa EpiWkZ vaoa WiilvaZ ql bilskZao lk, WkZ bfkWiiy skqWkdia qeafo
qolsXiap blo qeajpaitap vfqelsq BaZaoWi fkqaobaoakYa. Ol fk qeWq
fkpqWkYa qefp BaZaoWi dsWoWkqaa lb W oamsXifYWk dltaokjakq moltaZ ql Xa
klq W taoy moWYqfYWi qefkd.(122) 
   Pea kawq lYYWpflk smlk vefYe qea Osmoaja rlsoq YlkpfZaoaZ qefp BaZaoWi
dsWoWkqaa vWp Wbqao qea doaWq rftfi SWo. Pea OqWqa lb PawWp WqqajmqaZ,
fk 1861, ql paYaZa. Dao dltaokjakq WkZ eao malmia vWdaZ vWo lk qea
QkfqaZ OqWqap blo blso yaWop. Ek 1865 pea vWp ltaoYlja Xy bloYa lb Wojp,
WkZ eao qaoofqloy vWp lYYsmfaZ Xy qea jfifqWoy bloYap lb qea QkfqaZ
OqWqap, WkZ eao dltaokjakq vWp qajmloWofiy WZjfkfpqaoaZ Xy moltfpflkWi
Wmmlfkqaap lb qea LoapfZakq lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap WkZ WbqaovWoZp Xy
dltaoklop WmmlfkqaZ skZao Wk WYq lb rlkdoapp, Xy W jfifqWoy YljjWkZao,
PawWp Xafkd W mWoq lb IfifqWoy ufpqofYq Jl. 5, YljmlpaZ lb PawWp WkZ
HlsfpfWkW, msopsWkq ql Wk AYq lb rlkdoapp lb IWoYe, 1867. A OqWqa
Ylktakqflk, WppajXiaZ skZao qea Wsqelofqy lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap fk 1866,
mWppaZ Wk loZfkWkYa illhfkd ql qea oaYltaoy lb YaoqWfk XlkZp WiiadaZ ql
Xailkd ql qea OqWqa, WkZ lka F. S. PeolYhjloqlk, W dltaoklo velj qeWq
Ylktakqflk eWZ aiaYqaZ, WsqelofzaZ qea Xofkdfkd lb qea psfq. Pvl
psXpansakq jfifqWoy dltaoklop, DWjfiqlk WkZ LaWpa, bsoqeao oWqfbfaZ qefp
WYqflk. Pea Xfii vWp Wk lofdfkWi Xfii bfiaZ Xy PawWp Wp W OqWqa fk qea
Osmoaja rlsoq, WkZ vefia qefp YlkZfqflk lb eao pqWqaellZ YlkqfksaZ fq
moWyaZ Wk fkgskYqflk YlkYaokfkd YaoqWfk XlkZp WkZ qeafo Zaiftaoy ql qea
OqWqa. Pea Zabakpa, Wjlkd lqeao qefkdp, nsapqflkaZ: 
   1. Pea Wsqelofqy lb qea mWoqfap kWjaZ ql molpaYsqa W psfq fk qea kWja
lb PawWp. 
   2. Pea ofdeq lb PawWp, Wbqao eao Ylsopa fk qea rftfi SWo, ql psa Wp
W OqWqa lb qea Qkflk. 
   Eq baii ql qea ilq lb refab FspqfYa reWpa ql ZaYfZa qea pqWqsp lb qea
OqWqap vefYe eWZ WqqajmqaZ ql paYaZa, Wbqao qeay vaoa YlknsaoaZ Xy qea
QkfqaZ OqWqap WkZ Xabloa qeay vaoa bsiiy oapqloaZ ql qeafo oaiWqflkp Wp
OqWqap lb qea Qkflk. Ek W doaWq lmfkflk qea bliilvfkd mlfkqp vaoa
ZaYfZaZ: 
   1. PeWq qea qaoj OqWqa, Wp spaZ fk qea rlkpqfqsqflk, jlpq boansakqiy
awmoappap qea YljXfkaZ fZaW lb malmia, qaoofqloy, WkZ dltaokjakq; W
mlifqfYWi Yljjskfqy lb boaa Yfqfzakp, lYYsmyfkd W qaoofqloy lb ZabfkaZ
XlskZWofap, WkZ lodWkfzaZ skZao W dltaokjakq pWkYqflkaZ WkZ ifjfqaZ Xy
W vofqqak Ylkpqfqsqflk, WkZ apqWXifpeaZ Xy qea Ylkpakq lb qea dltaokaZ.
   2. PeWq qea Qkflk lb qeapa OqWqap skZao W Yljjlk rlkpqfqsqflk, blojfkd
W ZfpqfkYq WkZ doaWqao mlifqfYWi skfq, fp qeWq vefYe vWp ZapfdkWqaZ Xy
qea rlkpqfqsqflk Wp qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, WkZ jWZa, lb qea malmia WkZ
OqWqap Yljmlpfkd fq, lka malmia WkZ lka Ylskqoy. 
   3. PeWq qea dsWoWkqaa ql ataoy OqWqa lb W oamsXifYWk bloj lb
dltaokjakq vWp W dsWoWkqaa ql qea malmia lb qeWq OqWqa. 
   4. PeWq qea Qkflk vWp fkZfpplisXia. 
   5. PeWq qea OqWqap kataoqXaiapp mlppappaZ W ofdeq lb paib-dltaojjakq,
pltaoafdkqy, boaaZlj, WkZ fkZamakZakYa, WkZ ataoy mlvao, gsofpZfYqflk,
WkZ ofdeq klq awmoappiy lo Xy bWfo fjmifYWqflk ZaiadWqaZ ql qea Qkflk;
qeWq vfqelsq qea OqWqap fk skflk qeaoa YlsiZ Xa kl psYe mlifqfYWi XlZy
Wp qea QkfqaZ OqWqap. 
   6. PeWq qea moapaotWqflk WkZ qea jWfkqakWkYa lb qeafo dltaokjakqp vWp
Wp jsYe vfqefk qea YWoa lb qea BaZaoWi Wsqelofqy Wp vWp qea moapaotWqflk
lb qea kWqflkWi dltaokjakq fqpaib. 
   7. PeWq qea QkfqaZ OqWqap vWp Wk fkZapqosYqfXia dltaokjakq lb
fkZapqosYqfXia OqWqap. 
   8. PeWq qea dsWoWkqaa lb oamsXifYWk dltaokjakq fk qea Qkflk, ql qea
OqWqa, vWp Wp XfkZfkd lk qea QkfqaZ OqWqap Wp qea dsWoWkqaa lb maomaqsWi
skflk, WkZ qeWq PawWp vWp akqfqiaZ ql qea maoblojWkYa lb qeWq dsWoWkqaa
Xy qea bfkWi WYq veaoaXy pea XaYWja W kav jajXao lb qea Qkflk. 
   9. PeWq eao Wqqajmq Wq paYappflk WkZ Wii WYqp fkqakZaZ ql dfta fq
abbaYq vaoa ksii. 
   10. PeWq qea OqWqa YlkqfksaZ ql awfpq Wp W jajXao lb qea Qkflk,
klqvfqepqWkZfkd fqp qajmloWoy dltaokjakq eWZ Xaak ZapqolyaZ ql moapaota
qea Qkflk. 
   11. PeWq qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, eWtfkd moapaotaZ fqp lvk awfpqakYa, vWp
akdWdaZ fk maoblojfkd fqp ansWiiy pWYoaZ lXifdWqflk ql moltfZa W
oamsXifYWk bloj lb dltaokjakq ql qea OqWqa. 
   12. PeWq qefp vWp W mlifqfYWi dsWoWkqaa ql Xa maoblojaZ Xy qea
