   13. PeWq rlkdoapp vWp ajmlvaoaZ ql gsZda lb qea vWyp WkZ jaWkp lb
WYYljmifpefkd,qeWq oapsiq, WkZ qea moltfpflkWi WkZ qajmloWoy jfifqWoy
