ilyWi oamsXifYWk OqWqa dltaokjakqp YlsiZ Xa lodWkfzaZ. 
   14. PeWq fq XaelltaZ qea gsZfYfWoy ql oaYldkfza qea YlkqfksWi
awfpqakYa lb qea paYaZfkd OqWqap Wp jajXaop lb qea Qkflk,
klqvfqepqWkZfkd qea qajmloWoy pspmakpflk lb qeafo oaiWqflkp ql qea Qkflk
Xy qea bloYa lb qea atakqp WXlta oabaooaZ ql. 
   Jl amfqlja lb qefp doaWq ZaYfpflk YWk Zl fq gspqfYa. Eq fp Wjlkd qea
jlpq isjfklsp awmlpfqflkp awqWkq lb qea tfqWi nsapqflkp lb vefYee fq
qoaWqp, WkZ vWp bliilvaZ qeakYabloqe fk ataoy ZamWoqjakq lb qea
