   Ek W iWqao YWpa qea mlfkq vWp jWZa qeWq qea bloj lb dltaokjakq lb W
OqWqa vWp klq oamsXifYWk fk qea pakpa dsWoWkqaaZ Xy qea rlkpqfqsqflk;
qeWq fp ql pWy, qeWq YaoqWfk OqWqa pqWqsqap fk qea boWja WkZ awaYsqflk
