OqWqa iWvp miWYaZ lk qeaj Xy qea efdeapq OqWqa Ylsoq.(124) 
   Ek W taoy oaYakq YWpa qea Osmoaja rlsoq, YWiiaZ smlk ql ZaYfZa smlk
qea YWpa lb oftWi YlkqapqWkqp blo qea lbbfYa lb dltaoklo lb W OqWqa,
ZaYifkaZ ql Zl pl, ZaYiWofkd qeWq fq vWp moa-ajfkakqiy W YWpa blo
ZaYfpflk Xy qea Ylsoq lb iWpq oaploq fk qea OqWqa. Seak qea BaZaoWi
dsWoWkqaa lbb W oamsXifYWk bloj lb dltaokvakq, WkZ qea TER AjakZjakq
vaoa fktlhaZ, fq ZfpjfppaZ qea Ylkqakqflk Xy ZaYiWofkd qeWq qea
