   Sa Ylja klv ql YlkpfZao qelpa ofdeqp, moftfiadap, WkZ fjjskfqfap lb
qea Yfqfzak dsWoWkqaaZ Xy qea aWoiy WjakZjakqp ql qea rlkpqfqsqflk. 
 
         Pea Ejjskfqy lb qea rfqfzak AdWfkpq Aky HWv lb 
         rlkdoapp NapmaYqfqfd Wk xpqWXifpejakq lb Naifdflk 
         lo LolefXfqfkd qea Boaa xwaoYfpa Peaoalb. 
         (AjakZjakq E.) 
 
   xfqeao Xy qea Xfii lb ofdeqp, qea Ylkpqfqsqflk, lo qea iWv, lb ataoy
OqWqa lb qea Qkflk, W pfjfiWo dsWoWkqaa fp dftak ql fqp Yfqfzakp,
YlkYaokfkd OqWqa iWvp. Pefp Zlap klq jaWk qeWq qea malmia afqeao lb qea
JWqflk lo lb qea OqWqa eliZ oaifdflk fk Ylkqajmq lo Zapfoa ql Xaifqqia
fq. Kk qea YlkqoWWoy, qea liZapq lb qea Xfiip lb ofdeqp YlkqWfkp
oataoakWqfWi oabaoakYap ql oaifdflk lo qea Zsqy vefYe va lvka ql lso
IWhao. Pea reofpqfWk oaifdflk vWp gsZfYfWiiy ZaYiWoaZ ql Xa W mWoq lb
qea Yljjlk iWv lb LakkpyitWkfW.(128) csq qea xkdifpe xpqWXifpeaZ resoYe
