apqWXifpeaZ resoYe. DakYa qea molefXfqflk WXlta paq bloqe.(129) 
   Pea bfopq YWpa Wofpfkd skZao qefp YiWspa fktlitaZ qea abbaYq lb qea
Ylkpqfqsqflkp, kWqflkWi WkZ OqWqa, WkZ iWvp akWYqaZ qeaoaskZao, smlk
molmaoqy lb qea xmfpYlmWi resoYe fk RfodfkfW. Pea YWpa Wolpa qlsYefkd
YaoqWfk YesoYe molmaoqy fk AiawWkZofW, vefYe Yfqy vWp Wq qeWq qfja fk
qea ufpqofYq lb rlisjXfW. Pea Ylsoq XaiZ qeWq qea oaifdflsp
apqWXifpejakq lb xkdiWkZ vWp WZlmqaZ, pl bWo Wp WmmifYWXia, fk qea
Ylilky lb RfodfkfW, WkZ qeWq qea boaaeliZ lb YesoYe iWkZp vWp fk qea
mWoplk; qeWq iadfpiWqfta doWkqp vaoa fooatlYWXia; qeWq qea AYq lb
RfodfkfW lb 1776, Ylkbfojfkd ql qea xmfpYlmWi resoaX, Wp psYYapplo lb
qea xpqWXifpeaZ resoaX, fqp ofdeqp ql iWkZp, vWp klq YlkqoWoy ql qea
OqWqa Ylkpqfqsqflk WkZ ZfZ klq fkbofkda Wky ofdeqp, Yftfi, mlifqfYWi,
lo oaifdflsp, skZao qea OqWqa Ylkpqfqsqflk; qeWq iWqao WYqp paahfkd ql
Zftapq qea xmfpYlmWi resoYe lb RfodfkfW lb molmaoqy WYnsfoaZ moatflsp
ql qea Natlisqflk vaoa ksii, aqY.(130) cy qefp ZaYfpflk, WkZ lqeaop
pfjfiWo fk lqeao OqWqap, qea xmfpYlmWi resoYe oaqWfkaZ jsYe molmaoqy fk
qea liZao Ylilkfap. 
   Pea Osmoaja rlsoq eWp eaiZ qeWq qea molefXfqflk WXlta Zlap klq jWha
dllZ qea miaW lb W maoplk WYYspaZ lb Wk lbbakpa WdWfkpq jloWifqy WkZ
ZaYakYy, qeWq ea eWp WYqaZ msopsWkq ql qea qakaqp lb efp oaifdflsp
Xaifab, vefYe vaoa qelpa lb W Ilojlk.(131) Eq vWp pWfZ, "Naifdflsp
boaaZlj fp dsWoWkqaaZ ataoyveaoa qeolsdelsq qea QkfqaZ OqWqap pl bWo Wp
YlkdoappflkWi fkqaobaoakYa fp YlkYaokaZ." rlkdoapp vWp ZamoftaZ lb Wii
iadfpiWqfta mlvao ltao jaoa lmfkflk, Xsq vWp iabq boaa ql oaWYe WYqflkp
vefYe vaoa tfliWqfta lb plYfWi Zsqfap lo psXtaopfta lb dllZ loZao.
"LliydWjy eWp WivWyp Xaak lZflsp Wjlkd qea kloqeaok WkZ vapqaok kWqflkp
lb xsolma, WkZ, skqfi qea apqWXifpejakq lb qea Ilojlk resoYe, vWp Wijlpq
awYispftaiy W baWqsoa lb qea ifba lb ApfWqfY WkZ lb AbofYWk malmia.' '
Pea iWv mskfpefkd mliydWjy vWp smeaiZ Wp fkqakZaZ ql moatakq W
maokfYflsp moWYqfYa, kl jWqqao veWq vWp qea Xaifab lb qea mWoqy akdWdfkd
fk fq Pea lmfkflk ZaiftaoaZ Xy refab FspqfYa SWfqa fp Xlqe fkqaoapqfkd
WkZ fkpqosYqfta WkZ ansWiiy WmmifYWXia ql lqeao oaifdflsp fjjloWifqfap
qeWk mliydWjy. 
   Ek W iWqao YWpa qea Osmoaja rlsoq ZaYiWoaZ qeWq XfdWjy WkZ mliydWjy
Woa Yofjap Xy qea iWvp lb qea QkfqaZ OqWqap, Xy qea iWvp lb EZWel, WkZ
