WZtlYWYy W qakaq lb oaifdflk fp ql lbbakZ qea Yljjlk pakpa lb jWkhfkZ;
qeWq W Yofja fp klka qea iapp psYe, klo iapp lZfljp, XaYWspa pWkYqflkaZ
Xy veWq Wky mWoqfYsiWo paYq jWy ZapfdkWqa Wp oaifdflk; WkZ qeWq qea
