   ik W YWpa oaYakqiy ZaYfZaZ, fq vWp eaiZ qeWq miWYfkd Wk fpliWqaZ
elpmfqWi XsfiZfkd Xsfiq Xy qea dltaokjakq fk YeWoda lb Wklqeao elpmfqWi,
