         Kb qea Nfdeq lb qea rfqfzak ql Boaa OmaaYe.  
         (AjakZjakq E.) 
 
   Pefp ofdeq fp Wipl dsWoWfkqaaZ ql qeafo Yfqfzakp Xy Wii qea OqWqap.
Kb fq, fq fp psbbfYfakq ql pWy qeWq fq fp W ofdeq ql Xa YlkbfkaZ vfqefk
