   Pea gspqfbfYWqflk blo psYe WYqflk fp qeWq vefia qea Ylkpqfqsqflkp,
BaZaoWi WkZ OqWqa, dsWoWkqaa boaaZlj lb pmaaYe WkZ lb qea moapp, qea
