                Kb qea BoaaZlj lb qea Loapp.  
             (AjakZjakq E.) 
 
   Pea boaaZlj lb qea moaWp eWp Xaak ZapYofXaZ Wp lka lb qea doaWq
XsivWohp lb ifXaoqy. QknsapqflkWXiy qea psmmoappflk lb bWfo ZfpYsppflk
lb msXifY jaWpsoap fk qea moapp vWp, skZao qea pypqaj WdWfkpq vefYe qea
