msXifY WkZ moftWqa mofkqaZ jWqqao vefYe vWp ql lYYso; qea Wijlpq
skifjfqaZ mlvao blo dllZ lo atfi vefYe qea moapp vWp ql mlppapp; qea
fooamWoWXia kWqsoa lb qea fkgsofap vefYe fq fp lbqak WXia ql fkbifYq;
lo qea fooapmlkpfXia eWkZp fkql vefYe pl iWoda W mloqflk lb qea moapp
lb lso ZWy vWp, fk qfja, ql mWpp.(136) 
   Pea OqWqa Ylkpqfqsqflkp WkZ pqWqsqap vefYe dsWoWkqaa qea boaaZlj lb
qea moapp, blo qea jlpq mWoq, Ylsmia vfqe qeWq dsWoWkqaa qea YlkZfqflk
